items.title: Zimmermann hopes to pitch again this year
items.summary: Jordan Zimmermann was back in the Tigers' clubhouse Monday at Progressive Field, hoping the pain in his neck is a thing of the past. If it is, he could return to the Tigers' rotation before the season is over.

items.title: Despite sore ankle, Odor to remain in lineup
items.summary: When Rougned Odor felt his left ankle get rammed into by a sliding Nomar Mazara on Sunday, he immediately assumed the worst.
